<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A parenting author has revealed the most 'bogan' baby names in Australia of 2020 - including Carryn, Klowee, Tygrrr, Jinx and Pistol.</p>

<p>Sabrina Rogers-Anderson, the author of The little book of BOGAN baby names, compiled a top 10 list of the unique names for boys and girls on birth certificates around the country.  </p>

<p>Carryn and Klowee are just some of the more unusual spellings of traditional names parents are using.</p>

<p>A parenting author has revealed the most 'bogan' baby names in Australia of 2020 - including Carryn, Klowee, Tygrrr and Pistol (stock image)</p>

